quote.p:
“That the Netherlands Government has declared its willingness to do
                        everything in its power to organise these elections in the third quarter of
                        1949;

“That the Netherlands Government wishes to transfer the sovereignty, as soon
                        as the above-mentioned measures have been carried out and, inasmuch as it
                        depends on this government, no later than 1950;

“That in order to achieve this, consultations are already taking place
                        between Indonesian federalists and prominent persons from Republican
                        circles;
